<page>
   <topic>A5.SYSTEM_COLOR_SET Function</topic>
   <syntax>.System_Color_Set(c systemcolorname,c color[,L refresh])</syntax>
   <arguments>
     <argument>
         <name>systemcolorname</name>
         <description>The new color alias.
</description>
     </argument>
     <argument>
         <name>color</name>
         <description>The name of a system color.
</description>
     </argument>
     <argument>
         <name>refresh</name>
         <description>Logical</description>
     </argument>
   </arguments>
   <description>Set a system defined color.</description>
   <discussion>
The A5.SYSTEM_COLOR_SET() method creates a color alias.
   </discussion>
   <example><![CDATA[
a5.System_Color_Set("Error", "Red")
]]></example>
   
   <see>
      <ref>Color Functions and  Methods</ref>
   </see>
  
</page>